
Comment:  Which P-flag and Mask-bits to set when a player changes status...
Comment:  The higher levels inherit bits from lower.

PflagApprentice:
  Exorcise Reset Emote Zap Resurrect Stats Goto WreckDoors
  SummonObj Weather Lock Trace Peace NoHassle ChScore;

PflagWizard:
  NoTrace NoSnoop NoZap NoSummon NoSteal NoMagic NoForce NoAlias MflagEdit
  ObjectEdit Snoop Heal AliasMob StartInvis ChLevel TitleEdit
  RoomEdit Clone;

MaskWizard:
  NoExorcise;

PflagArchWizard:
  UAFInfo PflagEdit AliasPlayers Raw Echo ShowUsers Frob
  ChMobData Load/Store;

PflagDemiGod:
  Syslog Shutdown;

PflagGod:
  MaskEdit;



